  "title": "Sales Engineer (Machinery/ Equipment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of providing technical consultation and service to customers to help solve their applications using company products in a variety of industries, selecting and promoting the proper company products/services for their application.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in coordinating account strategy and contribute to territory’s strategic plan.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in coordinating off-site seminars and trade shows as needed.</li>\n  <li>In charge of responding promptly and efficiently to customer requests.</li>\n  <li>In charge of delivering growth in market share within assigned sales territory.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in securing new customers consistently and efficiently.</li>\n  <li>In charge of managing day-to-day activities .</li>\n  <li>Successfully implement new product-launch strategies</li>\n  <li>Other duties or projects, as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Degree in Engineering / Business or related field</li>\n  <li>Min 1 years of relevant experience in doing sales in Equipment/ Machinery Industry</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid Class 3 driving license is required</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
